        <h3 class="center ProductReview-title" tabindex="">
             
                <a rel="sponsored noreferrer noopener nofollow"
                   href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B07KGJ48VK?ie=UTF8&amp;linkCode=xm2&tag=bcavlat-20"
                   target="_blank">
             
                Kohler Forte Shower Head - Best Shower Head Overall
             </a>
        </h3>
    

    
      <div class="RichTextBody body-2">
          <ps-toggler data-toggle="review" class="ToggleText " itemprop="description" data-fade-out="true">
    
        <div data-toggle-content
            data-size="large"
            class="ToggleText-content body-1">
            <p>The Kohler Forte wins our best-rated award because it’s one of the top showerheads on the market. It offers three settings to help you have the best shower experience. Although it has fewer spray settings than the Waterpik Powerpulse and the Kohler Flipside, the Kohler Forte spray settings offer a better experience. These different spray settings allow you to customize your shower just how you like it.</p>

<div class="row ProductReview-injectedProsCons">
    
        <ul class="ProductReview-pros">
            
                <li>
                        <span>
                            <svg class="plus-circle-icon">
