<p>The full-coverage spray setting is ideal for everyday use. It provides broad and even spray coverage for the entire body, making it easy to rinse shampoo and soap. The silk spray option provides a luxurious rinsing experience that feels like soft and gentle rain — and the pulsating massage is perfect for easing aches and pains.</p><p>The Kohler Forte is also easy to install, making it an ideal option for those who don’t want to hire a plumber. It features a universal design that fits most shower arms, and its tool-free installation process makes it easy to install and remove. This showerhead comes in six different color options to match your aesthetics perfectly. It brings a modern style to any bathroom. It’s highly durable and made from high-quality materials to ensure longevity. Its corrosion-resistant finish prevents rust and tarnishing, so you can enjoy your showerhead for a long time.</p><p><b>Water usage:</b> 2.5 gallons per minute flow rate<br><b>Water pressure:</b> Strong and consistent flow<br><b>Variable settings:</b> 3 settings <br><b>Cleaning:</b> Easy to clean<br><b>Assembly/installation:</b> Wall-mounted<br><b>Looks and options:</b> Available in 6 colors</p><p><b>Price:</b> $$</p>
